dataIdInfo.envirDesc: Microsoft Windows 7 Version 6.1 (Build 7601) Service Pack 1; Esri ArcGIS 10.6.1.9270

dataExt.exDesc: Worked on intermittenly from January to November 2019

dataIdInfo.idAbs: This layer contains Places of Worship in Massachusetts, including churches, synagogues, and mosques. Places appearing in this layer are those overseen by the Massachusetts Council of Churches, Massachusetts Roman Catholic Dioceses, Synagogue Council of MA, or Islamic Council of New England. MassGIS generated the dataset by address-matching (geocoding) place of worship data. Whenever possible, development locations were manually refined using the most current Google Imagery. Internet sources were also used to refine locations.
dataIdInfo.idCredit: Masachusetts Council of Churches (http://www.masscouncilofchurches.org/) Roman Catholic Diocese in MA (http://www.usccb.org/about/bishops-and-dioceses/all-dioceses.cfm?zip=&specificstate=MA) Synagogue Council of Massachusetts (http://www.synagoguecouncil.org/) Islamic Council of New England (http://islamiccouncilne.org/)

attrdomv.udom: Sequential unique whole numbers that are automatically generated.

attr.attrdef: Name of the place of worship
Place of worship’s city or town
Place of worship’s main phone number
Name of place of worship’s religious leader
Year the place of worship was established
Denomination. For churches, the sect of Christianity
Identifies place of worship type: Church Mosque Synagogue
Source that provided the place of worship’s data

dataLineage.statement: This is the first release of this layer by MassGIS

prcStep.stepDesc: For this original layer, MassGIS generated a dataset by address-matching (geocoding) place of worship data. Whenever possible, development locations were manually refined using the most current Google Imagery. Internet sources were also used to refine locations.

report.measDesc: Data was requested from the Massachusetts Council of Churches, Massachusetts Roman Catholic Dioceses, Synagogue Council of MA, or Islamic Council of New England. In some cases spreadsheets were provided, in others data was compiled from directories on the websites.

Any places of worship not overseen by the Massachusetts Council of Churches, Massachusetts Roman Catholic Dioceses, Synagogue Council of MA, or Islamic Council of New England were not included in this dataset.
